= Iterations
== Iteration 0:
wrekad (wrekavoc daemon) starts and can answer queries sent from wrekavoc (client) using REST
wrekavoc uses restclient and optparse for command line parsing
wrekad uses sinatra
wrekanode (wrekavoc node daemon) starts and can answer queries sent from wrekad
wrekad can send queries to wrekanode

== Iteration 1:
LXC creation using fixed IP addresses

== Iteration 2:
IP address allocation + tests

== Iteration 3:
network links + routing setup

== Infrastructure:
* Add gemspec and do the work so that Wrekavoc can be installed as a Gem
* Prepare Debian package for Wrekavoc
* Infrastructure for unit tests

== Implementation
Add /vnodes/destroy in the API
